00:08:47.120 --> 00:08:48.039
Ako ay walang iba kundi isang kahihiyan.

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:48.919
ano sabi mo

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.000
Ikaw palagi

00:08:50.679 --> 00:08:51.679
tanggalin mo ako.

00:08:52.279 --> 00:08:53.440
anak mo ako,

00:08:53.639 --> 00:08:55.039
ngunit hindi mo ako binigyan ng mukha.

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:57.039
Dahil hindi mo pinapaboran ang aking ina.

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:57.960
Ikaw lang ang bahala...

00:09:02.159 --> 00:09:02.759
Gobernador,

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:04.120
huminahon ka.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:05.519
